{"tid":1611920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[招人才]錦田區巴打要人呀!!","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:34:20.000Z","uid":286330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e500b1018c5d3f9356e507fa0908571aafa6e880","tid":1611920,"uid":286330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲手足，我係李頌慈Chris，將會積極考慮參選元朗區議會M37錦田選區，呢邊區議員鄧卓然已經自動當選左三屆，實在需要改變。我希望可以為錦田區出一分力，改變現狀，希望呢次選舉可以令居民明白「有得揀，先係老闆！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一隻手並拍唔得響，我好需要各方力量支持，有一班目標一致的團隊，先能夠成就大事。現招募各方人才加入，希望團隊得以壯大！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招募表格: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/volunteerwanted\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fvolunteerwanted&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=77ba5668\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/volunteerwanted</a><br />\n<br />\n如果想了解更多可入tg group: <a href=\"https://t.me/m37brosis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fm37brosis&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=ce3d0ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/m37brosis</a>"},{"pid":"8e8a275a3af1a2bb3d7bf698ba7e6f902885d282","tid":1611920,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"090684b0180b15e6b780d0a6baa399ee10bd4430","tid":1611920,"uid":54086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d886c66d063aad977ea1f34563747faa1eb03a","tid":1611920,"uid":54001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e33a2d19b9c36f6dbe607923245498cf31709f2","tid":1611920,"uid":182933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab0832ca5c36001e2abb826b92347fbaaadd558c","tid":161